tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE virtual_classroom_resources (
    id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    video_url VARCHAR,
    presentation_url VARCHAR,
    interactive_tool_url VARCHAR
)

CREATE TABLE videos (
    video_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    video_title VARCHAR(255),
    video_url TEXT,
    uploader_id INT,
    upload_date TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE presentations (
    presentation_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    presentation_title VARCHAR(255),
    presentation_file_path TEXT,
    presenter_id INT,
    upload_date TIMESTAMP
);
